title: Heat and Mass Transfer on MHD in the Oscillatory Flow of Viscoelastic Fluid between Two Plates with Heat Generation and Chemical Reaction
content: In this chapter we study the unstudy effect on MHD preamble porous medium through with thermal absorption and heat generation in the oscillatory flow of visco-elastic fluid between two plates in the presence of Chemical reaction. The expressions for the velocity, temperature and concentration distributions are arthemitiaclly solved by perturbation method.
